reports.title: ACTIVOS/ORG
reports.query:
MATCH t=((o:ORG)-[:HAS_SEG]->(seg:SEG)-[:HAS_SUBNET]->(sub:Subred)-[:HAS_IP]->(ip:IP))
RETURN o.org AS Organización, COUNT(DISTINCT ip.IP) AS Activos

reports.title: Porcentaje de nodos con capturas
reports.query:
MATCH (o:ORG)-[:HAS_SEG]->(seg:SEG)-[:HAS_SUBNET]->(sub:Subred)-[:HAS_IP]->(ip:IP)-[:HAS_PORT]->(p:Port)
WITH o, COUNT(DISTINCT ip) AS totalNodos, COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN p.Screenshot IS NOT NULL THEN p END) AS nodosConRelacion
RETURN o.org AS ORGANIZACIÓN, 
       toString(round(nodosConRelacion * 100.0 / totalNodos, 2)) + '%' AS CAPTURAS

reports.title: ACTIVOS IGUALES DESCUBIERTOS EN DISTINTAS ORGANIZACIOONES BASADO EN LAS CAPTURAS DE PANTALLA
reports.query:
MATCH t=((o1:ORG)-[:HAS_SEG]->(seg:SEG)-[:HAS_SUBNET]->(sub:Subred)-[:HAS_IP]->(ip:IP)-[:HAS_PORT]->(p:Port)),
      ((o2:ORG)-[:HAS_SEG]->(seg2:SEG)-[:HAS_SUBNET]->(sub2:Subred)-[:HAS_IP]->(ip2:IP)-[:HAS_PORT]->(p2:Port))
WHERE p.org <> p2.org 
AND p.Screenshot IS NOT NULL 
AND p2.Screenshot IS NOT NULL 
AND p.Screenshot = p2.Screenshot
AND p.Screenshot <> '' 
AND p2.Screenshot <> ''
RETURN t

reports.title: IPS VISIBLES DESDE MÚLTIPLES SEGMENTOS (PIVOTE)

WHERE (ip1.ip = ip2.ip) AND (o.org = $neodash_org_org)
RETURN t
